      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Watertown%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Watertown once hosted the Iroquois passenger train, the last sleeper service to the city, which ended in 1961.",
